title: Dreams of Darkchylde Vol. 1 (Digital) (Minutemen-The Undead)
description:
Dreams of Darkchylde

English | CBR | 1 Issue

Genre: Fantasy, Horror

Written by Randy Queen
Art by Randy Queen, Ron Adrian and Brandon Peterson

Collects DREAMS OF DARKCHYLDE #1-6!

Ariel Chylde is the girl cursed to become any of the creatures from her many Nightmares. But have the shadows circled all her life? Now we go deeper. Into her past. Into her dreams. Where fears roam, and truth is never a friend. New Collection and Cover by RANDY QUEEN.
